# Build with one thread per CPU core at the module (reactor) level.
# This parallelises independent modules (catalog, negotiation, tools, data-transfer)
# and stacks on top of the Surefire parallel=classes configuration in pom.xml
# which parallelises test classes within each module.
#
# Override on the CLI if needed:  mvn package -T 1  (sequential)
-T1C
